ch.njol.skript.bukkitutil

Class UnresolvedOfflinePlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.njol.skript.bukkitutil.UnresolvedOfflinePlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable, org.bukkit.entity.AnimalTamer, org.bukkit.OfflinePlayer, org.bukkit.permissions.ServerOperator

    public class UnresolvedOfflinePlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.OfflinePlayer
    An OfflinePlayer that has only a name but no UUID set.

    Should only be used in Commands and the parser for offline players.

    Will produce NullPointerExceptions if used incorrectly.
